am","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/fm/DBMG/Pages/GraduateProgram.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-26"},{"source_id":"aub_fm_epim_ms_program","page_title":"MS Program","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/fm/EPIM/Pages/MS-Program.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-26"},{"source_id":"aub_fm_pharm_ms_program","page_title":"Masters Program","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/fm/PharmacologyandToxicology/Pages/MS-Program.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-26"},{"source_id":"aub_graduate_council","page_title":"Graduate Council","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/graduatecouncil/Pages/default.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_hson_home","page_title":"Rafic Hariri School of Nursing","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/hson/Pages/default.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-26"},{"source_id":"aub_hson_msn_handbook","page_title":"MSN Graduate Student Handbook 2025-2026","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/hson/Documents/MSN-handbook.pdf","date_accessed":"2026-06-26"},{"source_id":"aub_hson_phd_handbook","page_title":"PhD Student Handbook 2025-26","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/hson/Documents/PhD-handbook-25-26.pdf","date_accessed":"2026-06-26"},{"source_id":"aub_iem","page_title":"Industrial Engineering and Management","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/msfea/iem/Pages/default.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_me","page_title":"Mechanical Engineering","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/msfea/me/Pages/default.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_msfea_home","page_title":"Maroun Semaan Faculty of Engineering and Architecture","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/msfea/Pages/default.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_osb_emba","page_title":"Executive MBA Programs","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/osb/Pages/embaprograms.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_osb_home","page_title":"Welcome to the Suliman S. Olayan School of Business","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/osb/Pages/default.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_osb_mba_costs_fees","page_title":"Costs and Fees","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/osb/MBA/Pages/Costs-and-Fees.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-26"},{"source_id":"aub_osb_mfin","page_title":"Master's in Finance Leading the future of finance","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/osb/MFIN/Pages/default.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_osb_mhrm","page_title":"Master's in Human Resource Management Developing and managing leaders of the future","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/osb/MHRM/Pages/default.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_osb_msba","page_title":"MSBA, the leading Business Analytics program in the MENA region Where business and big data meet","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/osb/MSBA/Pages/default.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_osb_omba","page_title":"MBA Online Suliman S. Olayan School of Business","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/osb/OMBA/Pages/default.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_osb_omba_admissions","page_title":"Admissions and Fees MBA Online","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/osb/OMBA/Pages/Admission.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_osb_omba_learning","page_title":"The Learning MBA Online","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/osb/OMBA/Pages/Learning.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_osb_omba_program","page_title":"The Program MBA Online","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/osb/OMBA/Pages/program.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_osb_specialized_masters","page_title":"Specialized Master's","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/osb/Pages/SpecializedMasters.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_registrar","page_title":"Office of the Registrar","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/registrar/Pages/default.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_scholarships","page_title":"Scholarships","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/faid/Pages/Scholarships.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_soad","page_title":"School of Architecture and Design","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/msfea/ard/Pages/default.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_student_tuition","page_title":"Student","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/comptroller/Pages/Student.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-25"},{"source_id":"aub_tuition_2026_2027","page_title":"Tuition Fees and Financial Aid","url":"https://www.aub.edu.lb/Pages/fees.aspx","date_accessed":"2026-06-26"}]$AUB$) AS src(
